<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to My First GitHub Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic styling to make it look clean and modern */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello, World! 👋</h1>
        <p>Welcome to my very first website hosted on GitHub Pages. I am excited to start building and sharing my web development journey here.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com" class="btn" target="_blank">Visit My GitHub</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
